title: Middle schooler 'threw wooden block at Trump motorcade'
text: Middle school student faces charges after 'confessing to hurling wooden block at Trump's motorcade' A vehicle in President Donald Trump's motorcade was struck by a '2x4' The incident happened Friday around 1:45 p.m in West Palm Beach, Florida Several members of the motorcade returned to the scene after completing the motorcade to look for witnesses and objects along the roadway A child from a local middle school confessed to throwing the wood at the motorcade, and also implicated four additional students
